Brings back so many good memories

On the app: Sometimes fails to show up (disappears right away or never disappears). These seems to be related to screen-orientation; clicking the list of open tasks, turning the phone sideways, and clicking the game app, usually fixes the problem. That seems to be what most of the bad reviews are complaining about, and it likely only affects some devices.  On the game: This is probably one of the greatest games for children (or people who used to be children XD) of all time. It's extremely creative, and it's clear that so much work was put into the animations. (there are so many animations; like, how even?) Best of all, you really need to think; these games are all about mind puzzles. Not like math puzzles, but actual problem solving; you need to pay attention to subtle details to figure out what you need to do.
